00:09:33.380 --> 00:09:34.870
And this is what
you start to see.

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:39.740
You start to see not just folks
like you, technological folks.

00:09:39.740 --> 00:09:41.110
Not just political folks.

00:09:41.110 --> 00:09:45.150
But you start to see people who
start wearing the B, the badge,

00:09:45.150 --> 00:09:47.670
as a symbol of something.

00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:51.380
And Megan's artwork I
thought was very interesting.

