writing about in 2013,

00:10:02.110 --> 00:10:05.080
was the cultural aspects of it.

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:05.850
Why?

00:10:05.850 --> 00:10:09.760
Why do you have people
coming around this idea

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:11.490
