00:26:01.980 --> 00:26:05.110
The transition from a
very passionate community

00:26:05.110 --> 00:26:08.250
of true believers, driven by
sort of maybe some libertarian

00:26:08.250 --> 00:26:10.750
ideas, and some
very strong views

00:26:10.750 --> 00:26:14.114
about kind of a utopian vision
for the world, newcomers.

00:26:14.114 --> 00:26:15.655
Those newcomers are
not necessarily--

00:26:15.655 --> 00:26:17.113
they're a very
different community,

00:26:17.113 --> 00:26:18.660
and they have a
corporate flavor.

00:26:18.660 --> 00:26:20.580
And that's a very
important issue

00:26:20.580 --> 00:26:24.090
for how we deal with the
structure, the infrastructure,

00:26:24.090 --> 00:26:27.080
of not just Bitcoin, but
cryptocurrencies generally.

00:26:27.080 --> 00:26:30.500
And you guys I think need
to think about this stuff.

00:26:30.500 --> 00:26:33.480
Anyway, I was
