00:49:34.110 --> 00:49:37.340
And the problem is that
it gets lost in a world

00:49:37.340 --> 00:49:39.990
that the rest of us
don't seem to understand.

00:49:39.990 --> 00:49:42.182
But it's critical.

00:49:42.182 --> 00:49:43.890
So I'm just going to
leave you with that.

00:49:43.890 --> 00:49:46.895
And there's the cover
